{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":6000,"text":"Hi."},{"time":8000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":10000,"text":"I did that for two reasons."},{"time":13000,"text":"First of all, I wanted to give you"},{"time":16000,"text":"a good visual first impression."},{"time":19000,"text":"But the main reason I did it is that"},{"time":22000,"text":"that's what happens to me when I'm forced to wear"},{"time":25000,"text":"a Lady Gaga skanky mic."}]},{"cues":[{"time":28000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":31000,"text":"I'm used to a stationary mic."},{"time":35000,"text":"It's the sensible shoe of public address."}]},{"cues":[{"time":38000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":44000,"text":"But you clamp this thing on my head, and something happens."},{"time":47000,"text":"I just become skanky."},{"time":50000,"text":"(Laughter) So I'm sorry about that."},{"time":54000,"text":"And I'm already off-message."}]},{"cues":[{"time":57000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":60000,"text":"Ladies and gentlemen,"},{"time":63000,"text":"I have devoted the past 25 years of my life"},{"time":67000,"text":"to designing books."},{"time":69000,"text":"(\"Yes, BOOKS. You know, the bound volumes with ink on paper."},{"time":71000,"text":"You cannot turn them off with a switch."},{"time":73000,"text":"Tell your kids.\")"},{"time":75000,"text":"It all sort of started as a benign mistake,"},{"time":79000,"text":"like penicillin. (Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":82000,"text":"What I really wanted"},{"time":85000,"text":"was to be a graphic designer"},{"time":87000,"text":"at one of the big design firms in New York City."},{"time":89000,"text":"But upon arrival there,"},{"time":92000,"text":"in the fall of 1986, and doing a lot of interviews,"},{"time":96000,"text":"I found that the only thing I was offered"},{"time":99000,"text":"was to be Assistant to the Art Director at Alfred A. Knopf,"},{"time":102000,"text":"a book publisher."},{"time":104000,"text":"Now I was stupid,"},{"time":107000,"text":"but not so stupid that I turned it down."}]},{"cues":[{"time":110000,"text":"I had absolutely no idea"},{"time":113000,"text":"what I was about to become part of,"},{"time":115000,"text":"and I was incredibly lucky."},{"time":117000,"text":"Soon, it had occurred to me what my job was."},{"time":121000,"text":"My job was to ask this question:"},{"time":124000,"text":"\"What do the stories look like?\""},{"time":125000,"text":"Because that is what Knopf is."},{"time":128000,"text":"It is the story factory, one of the very best in the world."},{"time":131000,"text":"We bring stories to the public."}]},{"cues":[{"time":134000,"text":"The stories can be anything,"},{"time":137000,"text":"and some of them are actually true."},{"time":139000,"text":"But they all have one thing in common:"},{"time":144000,"text":"They all need to look like something."},{"time":147000,"text":"They all need a face."},{"time":150000,"text":"Why? To give you a first impression"},{"time":154000,"text":"of what you are about to get into."},{"time":157000,"text":"A book designer gives form to content,"},{"time":161000,"text":"but also"},{"time":163000,"text":"manages a very careful balance between the two."}]},{"cues":[{"time":166000,"text":"Now, the first day"},{"time":168000,"text":"of my graphic design training at Penn State University,"},{"time":171000,"text":"the teacher, Lanny Sommese, came into the room"},{"time":174000,"text":"and he drew a picture of an apple on the blackboard,"},{"time":177000,"text":"and wrote the word \"Apple\" underneath,"},{"time":179000,"text":"and he said, \"OK. Lesson one. Listen up.\""},{"time":182000,"text":"And he covered up the picture and he said,"},{"time":185000,"text":"\"You either say this,\" and then he covered up the word,"},{"time":188000,"text":"\"or you show this."},{"time":191000,"text":"But you don't do this.\""},{"time":194000,"text":"Because this is treating your audience like a moron."},{"time":199000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":202000,"text":"And they deserve better."}]},{"cues":[{"time":205000,"text":"And lo and behold, soon enough,"},{"time":207000,"text":"I was able to put this theory to the test"},{"time":210000,"text":"on two books that I was working on for Knopf."},{"time":214000,"text":"The first was Katharine Hepburn's memoirs,"},{"time":218000,"text":"and the second was a biography of Marlene Dietrich."},{"time":221000,"text":"Now the Hepburn book"},{"time":224000,"text":"was written in a very conversational style,"},{"time":227000,"text":"it was like she was sitting across a table telling it all to you."},{"time":230000,"text":"The Dietrich book was an observation"},{"time":233000,"text":"by her daughter; it was a biography."},{"time":235000,"text":"So the Hepburn story is words"},{"time":238000,"text":"and the Dietrich story is pictures, and so we did this."},{"time":242000,"text":"So there you are."},{"time":245000,"text":"Pure content and pure form, side by side."},{"time":248000,"text":"No fighting, ladies."}]},{"cues":[{"time":251000,"text":"(\"What's a Jurassic Park?\")"},{"time":253000,"text":"Now, what is the story here?"},{"time":256000,"text":"Someone"},{"time":259000,"text":"is re-engineering dinosaurs"},{"time":262000,"text":"by extracting their DNA"},{"time":265000,"text":"from prehistoric amber."},{"time":268000,"text":"Genius!"},{"time":271000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":275000,"text":"Now, luckily for me,"},{"time":278000,"text":"I live and work in New York City,"},{"time":280000,"text":"where there are plenty of dinosaurs."},{"time":282000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":285000,"text":"So,"},{"time":289000,"text":"I went to the Museum of Natural History,"},{"time":291000,"text":"and I checked out the bones, and I went to the gift shop,"},{"time":295000,"text":"and I bought a book."},{"time":296000,"text":"And I was particularly taken with this page of the book,"},{"time":300000,"text":"and more specifically the lower right-hand corner."}]},{"cues":[{"time":304000,"text":"Now I took this diagram,"},{"time":307000,"text":"and I put it in a Photostat machine,"},{"time":311000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":317000,"text":"and I took a piece of tracing paper,"},{"time":320000,"text":"and I taped it over the Photostat"},{"time":324000,"text":"with a piece of Scotch tape -- stop me if I'm going too fast --"},{"time":327000,"text":"(Laughter) --"},{"time":334000,"text":"and then I took a Rapidograph pen --"},{"time":337000,"text":"explain it to the youngsters --"},{"time":340000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":343000,"text":"and I just started to reconstitute the dinosaur."}]},{"cues":[{"time":347000,"text":"I had no idea what I was doing,"},{"time":350000,"text":"I had no idea where I was going,"},{"time":352000,"text":"but at some point, I stopped --"},{"time":354000,"text":"when to keep going would seem like I was going too far."},{"time":358000,"text":"And what I ended up with was a graphic representation"},{"time":362000,"text":"of us seeing this animal coming into being."},{"time":366000,"text":"We're in the middle of the process."},{"time":368000,"text":"And then I just threw some typography on it."},{"time":371000,"text":"Very basic stuff,"},{"time":373000,"text":"slightly suggestive of public park signage."},{"time":376000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":382000,"text":"Everybody in house loved it,"},{"time":384000,"text":"and so off it goes to the author."},{"time":386000,"text":"And even back then,"},{"time":388000,"text":"Michael was on the cutting edge."},{"time":390000,"text":"(\"Michael Crichton responds by fax:\")"},{"time":394000,"text":"(\"Wow! Fucking Fantastic Jacket\")"},{"time":396000,"text":"(Laughter) (Applause)"},{"time":403000,"text":"That was a relief to see that pour out of the machine."},{"time":407000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":410000,"text":"I miss Michael."}]},{"cues":[{"time":413000,"text":"And sure enough, somebody from MCA Universal"},{"time":416000,"text":"calls our legal department to see if they can"},{"time":419000,"text":"maybe look into buying the rights to the image,"},{"time":421000,"text":"just in case they might want to use it."},{"time":424000,"text":"Well, they used it."},{"time":427000,"text":"(Laughter) (Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":432000,"text":"And I was thrilled."},{"time":435000,"text":"We all know it was an amazing movie,"},{"time":437000,"text":"and it was so interesting to see it"},{"time":439000,"text":"go out into the culture and become this phenomenon"},{"time":443000,"text":"and to see all the different permutations of it."},{"time":446000,"text":"But not too long ago,"},{"time":449000,"text":"I came upon this on the Web."},{"time":452000,"text":"No, that is not me."},{"time":455000,"text":"But whoever it is,"},{"time":458000,"text":"I can't help but thinking they woke up one day like,"},{"time":461000,"text":"\"Oh my God, that wasn't there last night. Ooooohh!"},{"time":464000,"text":"I was so wasted.\""},{"time":467000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":470000,"text":"But if you think about it, from my head"},{"time":473000,"text":"to my hands to his leg."},{"time":476000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":481000,"text":"That's a responsibility."},{"time":484000,"text":"And it's a responsibility that I don't take lightly."},{"time":487000,"text":"The book designer's responsibility is threefold:"},{"time":490000,"text":"to the reader, to the publisher and, most of all, to the author."},{"time":494000,"text":"I want you to look at the author's book"},{"time":497000,"text":"and say, \"Wow! I need to read that.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":500000,"text":"David Sedaris is one of my favorite writers,"},{"time":503000,"text":"and the title essay"},{"time":506000,"text":"in this collection is about his trip to a nudist colony."},{"time":509000,"text":"And the reason he went is because"},{"time":511000,"text":"he had a fear of his body image,"},{"time":513000,"text":"and he wanted to explore what was underlying that."},{"time":516000,"text":"For me, it was simply an excuse to design a book"},{"time":519000,"text":"that you could literally take the pants off of."},{"time":522000,"text":"But when you do,"},{"time":525000,"text":"you don't get what you expect."},{"time":527000,"text":"You get something that goes much deeper than that."},{"time":529000,"text":"And David especially loved this design"},{"time":533000,"text":"because at book signings, which he does a lot of,"},{"time":536000,"text":"he could take a magic marker and do this."},{"time":539000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":545000,"text":"Hello!"},{"time":548000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":551000,"text":"Augusten Burroughs wrote a memoir"},{"time":554000,"text":"called [\"Dry\"], and it's about his time in rehab."},{"time":557000,"text":"In his 20s, he was a hotshot ad executive,"},{"time":562000,"text":"and as Mad Men has told us, a raging alcoholic."},{"time":565000,"text":"He did not think so, however,"},{"time":568000,"text":"but his coworkers did an intervention and they said,"},{"time":571000,"text":"\"You are going to rehab, or you will be fired and you will die.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":575000,"text":"Now to me, this was always going to be a typographic solution,"},{"time":579000,"text":"what I would call the opposite of Type 101."},{"time":581000,"text":"What does that mean?"},{"time":583000,"text":"Usually on the first day of Introduction to Typography,"},{"time":585000,"text":"you get the assignment of, select a word"},{"time":588000,"text":"and make it look like what it says it is. So that's Type 101, right?"},{"time":591000,"text":"Very simple stuff."},{"time":593000,"text":"This is going to be the opposite of that."},{"time":596000,"text":"I want this book to look like it's lying to you,"},{"time":599000,"text":"desperately and hopelessly, the way an alcoholic would."}]},{"cues":[{"time":603000,"text":"The answer was the most low-tech thing you can imagine."},{"time":606000,"text":"I set up the type, I printed it out on an Epson printer"},{"time":610000,"text":"with water-soluble ink, taped it to the wall"},{"time":613000,"text":"and threw a bucket of water at it. Presto!"},{"time":616000,"text":"Then when we went to press,"},{"time":618000,"text":"the printer put a spot gloss on the ink"},{"time":620000,"text":"and it really looked like it was running."}]},{"cues":[{"time":622000,"text":"Not long after it came out, Augusten was waylaid in an airport"},{"time":625000,"text":"and he was hiding out in the bookstore"},{"time":627000,"text":"spying on who was buying his books."},{"time":629000,"text":"And this woman came up to it,"},{"time":632000,"text":"and she squinted, and she took it to the register,"},{"time":634000,"text":"and she said to the man behind the counter, \"This one's ruined.\""},{"time":637000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":641000,"text":"And the guy behind the counter said, \"I know, lady. They all came in that way.\""},{"time":646000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":651000,"text":"Now, that's a good printing job."}]},{"cues":[{"time":654000,"text":"A book cover"},{"time":657000,"text":"is a distillation."},{"time":660000,"text":"It is a haiku,"},{"time":663000,"text":"if you will, of the story."},{"time":666000,"text":"This particular story"},{"time":669000,"text":"by Osama Tezuka"},{"time":672000,"text":"is his epic life of the Buddha,"},{"time":675000,"text":"and it's eight volumes in all. But the best thing is"},{"time":678000,"text":"when it's on your shelf, you get a shelf life"},{"time":682000,"text":"of the Buddha, moving from one age to the next."},{"time":689000,"text":"All of these solutions"},{"time":692000,"text":"derive their origins from the text of the book,"},{"time":696000,"text":"but once the book designer has read the text,"},{"time":699000,"text":"then he has to be an interpreter"},{"time":702000,"text":"and a translator."}]},{"cues":[{"time":705000,"text":"This story was a real puzzle."},{"time":708000,"text":"This is what it's about."},{"time":711000,"text":"(\"Intrigue and murder among 16th century Ottoman court painters.\")"}]},{"cues":[{"time":714000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":717000,"text":"All right, so I got a collection of the paintings together"},{"time":721000,"text":"and I looked at them and I deconstructed them"},{"time":723000,"text":"and I put them back together."},{"time":725000,"text":"And so, here's the design, right?"},{"time":727000,"text":"And so here's the front and the spine, and it's flat."},{"time":730000,"text":"But the real story starts when you wrap it around a book and put it on the shelf."}]},{"cues":[{"time":733000,"text":"Ahh! We come upon them,"},{"time":737000,"text":"the clandestine lovers. Let's draw them out."},{"time":740000,"text":"Huhh! They've been discovered by the sultan."},{"time":745000,"text":"He will not be pleased."},{"time":748000,"text":"Huhh! And now the sultan is in danger."},{"time":751000,"text":"And now, we have to open it up"},{"time":754000,"text":"to find out what's going to happen next."},{"time":757000,"text":"Try experiencing that on a Kindle."},{"time":760000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":767000,"text":"Don't get me started."},{"time":770000,"text":"Seriously."},{"time":773000,"text":"Much is to be gained by eBooks:"},{"time":777000,"text":"ease, convenience, portability."},{"time":780000,"text":"But something is definitely lost: tradition,"},{"time":783000,"text":"a sensual experience, the comfort of thingy-ness --"},{"time":788000,"text":"a little bit of humanity."}]},{"cues":[{"time":791000,"text":"Do you know what John Updike used to do"},{"time":794000,"text":"the first thing when he would get a copy"},{"time":796000,"text":"of one of his new books from Alfred A. Knopf?"},{"time":798000,"text":"He'd smell it."},{"time":801000,"text":"Then he'd run his hand over the rag paper,"},{"time":805000,"text":"and the pungent ink and the deckled edges of the pages."},{"time":808000,"text":"All those years, all those books, he never got tired of it."},{"time":813000,"text":"Now, I am all for the iPad,"},{"time":817000,"text":"but trust me -- smelling it will get you nowhere."},{"time":821000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":824000,"text":"Now the Apple guys are texting,"},{"time":827000,"text":"\"Develop odor emission plug-in.\""},{"time":830000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":835000,"text":"And the last story I'm going to talk about is quite a story."},{"time":838000,"text":"A woman"},{"time":841000,"text":"named Aomame in 1984 Japan finds herself"},{"time":844000,"text":"negotiating down a spiral staircase"},{"time":847000,"text":"off an elevated highway. When she gets to the bottom,"},{"time":850000,"text":"she can't help but feel that, all of a sudden,"},{"time":852000,"text":"she's entered a new reality"},{"time":854000,"text":"that's just slightly different from the one that she left,"},{"time":857000,"text":"but very similar, but different."},{"time":859000,"text":"And so, we're talking about parallel planes of existence,"},{"time":862000,"text":"sort of like a book jacket and the book that it covers."}]},{"cues":[{"time":866000,"text":"So how do we show this?"},{"time":869000,"text":"We go back to Hepburn and Dietrich, but now we merge them."},{"time":873000,"text":"So we're talking about different planes, different pieces of paper."},{"time":877000,"text":"So this is on a semi-transparent piece of velum."},{"time":880000,"text":"It's one part of the form and content."},{"time":883000,"text":"When it's on top of the paper board,"},{"time":886000,"text":"which is the opposite, it forms this."},{"time":889000,"text":"So even if you don't know anything about this book,"},{"time":893000,"text":"you are forced to consider a single person"},{"time":896000,"text":"straddling two planes of existence."},{"time":899000,"text":"And the object itself invited exploration"},{"time":904000,"text":"interaction, consideration"},{"time":909000,"text":"and touch."}]},{"cues":[{"time":912000,"text":"This debuted at number two"},{"time":914000,"text":"on the New York Times Best Seller list."},{"time":916000,"text":"This is unheard of,"},{"time":918000,"text":"both for us the publisher, and the author."},{"time":920000,"text":"We're talking a 900-page book"},{"time":922000,"text":"that is as weird as it is compelling,"},{"time":924000,"text":"and featuring a climactic scene"},{"time":926000,"text":"in which a horde of tiny people"},{"time":928000,"text":"emerge from the mouth of a sleeping girl"},{"time":930000,"text":"and cause a German Shepherd to explode."},{"time":932000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":940000,"text":"Not exactly Jackie Collins."},{"time":943000,"text":"Fourteen weeks on the Best Seller list,"},{"time":946000,"text":"eight printings, and still going strong."}]},{"cues":[{"time":949000,"text":"So even though we love publishing as an art,"},{"time":952000,"text":"we very much know it's a business too,"},{"time":955000,"text":"and that if we do our jobs right and get a little lucky,"},{"time":958000,"text":"that great art can be great business."}]},{"cues":[{"time":961000,"text":"So that's my story. To be continued."},{"time":964000,"text":"What does it look like?"},{"time":967000,"text":"Yes. It can, it does and it will,"},{"time":972000,"text":"but for this book designer,"},{"time":975000,"text":"page-turner,"},{"time":978000,"text":"dog-eared place-holder,"},{"time":981000,"text":"notes in the margins-taker,"},{"time":984000,"text":"ink-sniffer,"},{"time":987000,"text":"the story looks like this."}]},{"cues":[{"time":991000,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":994000,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}